Pantheon Voxel Field Engine — MVP

What it does

Takes a set of locations, scores them as voxels, and ranks where an idea is most likely to work.

For V1, each voxel is just a neighborhood cell with:
	•	traffic
	•	competition
	•	price
	•	rating
	•	narrative tag
	•	your skill modifier

Then it outputs:
	•	raw score
	•	adjusted score
	•	rank
	•	simple recommendation

