Scoring logic

Base equation:

score = (traffic * rating) / (competition * price)

Adjusted for your edge:

true_score = score * skill_modifier

Narrative multiplier:
	•	growing = 1.10
	•	trendy = 1.08
	•	up-and-coming = 1.15
	•	stable = 1.00
	•	declining = 0.85
	•	elite = 0.95
	•	underground = 1.05

Final:

final_score = true_score * narrative_multiplier


