The simplest real use case

Start with this exact question:

“Where in Raleigh would a new concept have the best chance if the operator is strong at branding and wants medium competition with rising attention?”

Then build the csv by hand with 10–20 rows.

You do not need APIs yet.
Manual data is enough to prove the concept.

⸻

Clean operator protocol
	1.	Pick one business type.
	2.	Choose 10–20 locations.
	3.	Score them manually.
	4.	Run ranking.
	5.	Check if the output feels true.
	6.	Adjust weights.
	7.	Repeat.

That loop is the product before the product.

