The deeper pattern

Project Silica stores information by changing structure in volume.

This engine does the same idea symbolically:
	•	each neighborhood is a voxel
	•	each voxel stores multi-dimensional state
	•	reading the city becomes reading a volume of encoded probability

So yes, this is basically:
Silica logic applied to markets and meaning.

